    "summary": "An out-of-bounds write vulnerability in FFmpeg's libavcodec library, specifically in the MagicYUV...",
    "details": "An out-of-bounds write vulnerability in FFmpeg's libavcodec library, specifically in the MagicYUV decoder, allows denial-of-service and, in some cases, can be exploited for remote code execution.\n\nThis vulnerability is associated with the file `libavcodec/magicyuv.C`.\n\nThis issue affects FFmpeg before version 8.1.2.",
    "severity": [
